  "description": {
   "en": "\"I really liked that voice—\"\n\nOn the day of the school entrance ceremony, Teppei Kodaira got absolutely charmed by the voice of Tsugumi Kuritani, who delivered a speech as the representative of the incoming freshman students. By complete coincidence, Teppei's seat in class was also right next to the owner of \"that voice\", Kuritani-san. But just when he thinks they'll gradually become closer...\n\nKuritani-san sends him a message: \"Teppei, it's embarrassing to let you hear my voice just for the sake of your reactions!\" Kodaira-kun wants to hear her voice, and Kuritani-san doesn't want to be heard by him. A frustrating and \"pure\" romcom between these two begins!!\n\n(Source: Comipo)\n\n---\n\nAdditional Links:\n\n* [Comipo](https://comipo.app/series/web/34749/) (Publisher)",
   "ja": "（本当に好きな声だった―――）\n小平 哲平は入学式の日、新入生代表挨拶をする栗谷つぐみの【声】に強く惹かれる。\n偶然にも哲平の席は、その【声】の女生徒、栗谷さんの隣の席だった。\n次第に距離が近づくか…と思いきや…―\n\n哲平のリアクションのために【声】を聞かせるのが恥ずかしい！と栗谷さんからのメッセージが…！\n声を聞きたい哲平と、声を聞かせたくない栗谷さん。\n二人のもどかしい“ピュア”ラブコメ開戦！！"
  },
